{"title":"战士诗歌","authors":["赵文彬"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":8,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士诗歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵文彬录"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整编（注一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说整编，道整编，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整编为了反攻战；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游击不能打大仗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野战攻城不费难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八一我们整编了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个同志面带笑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你练武，我磨刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三大技术（注二）要学好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级觉悟都提高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打下冀中的平、津、保，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国武器使一使，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"功劳簿上把名标。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注一）当解放战争接近反攻时，分散的地方的游击部队已不适合新的战争需要，必须实行整编，这是冀中某旅整编时战士所作的快板。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注二）即射击、爆破、投弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地雷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地雷黑又大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老蒋真害怕；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰隆一声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人缴了枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地雷大，像西瓜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不生根，不长芽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碰上匪军就开花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导员，真是棒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮助我，扛机枪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房子少，院里睡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑夜他把碾子推；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打早起，就挑水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全连谁也不掉队。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放区，真是强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众好比爹和娘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又烧水，又做饭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腾了屋子还扫炕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿童团，唱着歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喊完口号就是“一、二、三”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大伯，真是沾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮助伙夫把油挑子担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志们脚上打了泡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村长忙把大车套，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄饽饽，红山药，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘一个一个往外端；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见一个，拿一块，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘把我袖子拉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫声同志别打呱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人是铁，饭是钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃块干粮打老蒋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民真是一条心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比着骨肉亲十分；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人心都是肉来长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立个大功报老乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工具"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打仗靠枪杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产靠工具，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要不爱它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"减少生产力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产当中记日记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万不要忘学习；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学写作，学识字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下地收工都集体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保持咱们的军风纪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李尧同志放羊歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公鸡咯咯的叫，天发亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李尧赶着羊儿出村庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手拿着鞭儿嘴里唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命军人去放羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想从前和如今不一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前是给地主把羊放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挨打挨骂饿肚肠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年只给一身破衣裳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今放羊自己的羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大生产我把羊儿放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳暖洋洋，暖洋洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放羊他不把学习忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习本，搁腿上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新民笔杆发黑亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄黄笔尖蓝蓝水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他比着羊儿来画羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大羊小羊花黧羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑羊白羊排成行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画完就把字来写，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要作学习的好榜样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野草儿青又黄，青又黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊儿吃草喷喷香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大路旁，山坡上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃草的声音嚓嚓地响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小羊??的把母羊叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母羊??的叫小羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小羊跑到母羊旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双腿跪下把奶尝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公羊一对一对的前腿站起来把头撞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大鞭子呱呱的响，呱呱的响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头羊四条腿儿跑的忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跑在群前去领路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四百只羊儿排成行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山沟的水，哗哗的响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊儿低头喝水忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊儿吃饱喝足了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳落在西山上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李尧举鞭赶着羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱唱喝喝的回村庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑夜李尧忙，李尧忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕天寒风又凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一宿起来好几趟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到羊圈里看看羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母羊??的叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下了一对小绵羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小羊才下不认奶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他挤下奶儿喂小羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又怕小羊受了冻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱到屋炕上去暖小羊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产把羊放，把羊放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放羊的李尧真是强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产计划订得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条一条写纸上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一条不怕天寒冷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二条保证羊肥胖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三条保证小羊活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四条保证圈不脏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后又写了一小句："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“放羊立功把名扬”。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}